    public class ShortestQueueDispatchingPolicy
extends ImplicitButNotExplicitInputOnlyDependentPolicy<java.util.List<UserQueue>,UserQueue>
    Implements the dispatching policy for a user reaching a multi-queue structure. The policy considers the shortest queue (in terms of number of enqueued users).
    Author:
    Daniele Ganni
